# Spurious ESM-flavoured action bundle.  action.yml uses dist/main.cjs; an
# accidental dist/main.js (e.g. from `esbuild --outfile=dist/main.js`) would
# be a stale duplicate that bypasses any gates added to the .cjs bundle.
